The expressions of the amplitudes associated to each left-and-right-dressed \
disjoint direct Feynman diagram are calculated in time representation.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8982551888079557`*^9, 3.898255239729643*^9}, {
  3.898585105046615*^9, 3.898585106550789*^9}, {3.9082561029832764`*^9, 
